#include <bits/stdc++.h>

using namespace std;

#define pb push_back
#define mp make_pair
#define ll long long int
#define s(x) scanf("%d", &x)
#define sl(x) scanf("%lld", &x)
#define mod 1000000007

int a[105];

int main()
{
    int t, n, i;
    bool doll;
    cin >> t;
    while (t--) {
        cin >> n;
        for (i = 0; i < n; ++i)
            cin >> a[i];
        sort(a, a+n);
        doll = true;
        for (i = 1; i < n; ++i) {
            if (a[i-1] == a[i])
                doll = false;
        }
        printf(doll ? "YES\n" : "NO\n");
    }
    return 0;
}
